  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the cod fish and cook until it is browned on all sides.",
    "Add the soy milk, mustard, paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to medium low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the fish and sauce over rice or with crusty bread.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley or cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
